.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
cr3 [\fI\-options\fP] [filename]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
CoolReader is an e\-book reader for various platforms.
.sp
Supported file formats include plain text, HTML, RTF, Microsoft Word
(.doc), Palm Pilot (.prc, .pdb, .pml, .mobi), FB2, and EPUB.
